name: Shimano 105 CS-R7000 11 Speed Cassette
description: This durable cassette provides the shift quality of more expensive options at the cost of a few grams. 11 speeds let you discover the optimal gearing setup for the terrain and to "tune" the bike for any specific application.Nickle-plated steel cogs are hardwearing.The 3 largest sprockets are mounted on an aluminum spiders to keep the weight low.Steel lockring included.
